170
00:09:53,444 --> 00:09:55,446
who I really am as

171
00:09:55,446 --> 00:09:57,448
Alyana Heartily-Ferrer.

172
00:09:58,032 --> 00:10:01,035
Before I tell Baby
Ae and my niece.

173
00:10:25,935 --> 00:10:27,024
Hi!

174
00:10:27,561 --> 00:10:28,938
You're Aemie, right?

175
00:10:31,023 --> 00:10:32,024
Can I sit here?

176
00:10:32,316 --> 00:10:33,276
Oh, sure.

177
00:10:35,069 --> 00:10:36,079
Wow.

178
00:10:37,154 --> 00:10:38,281
You know me?

179
00:10:41,367 --> 00:10:42,345
Mmm.

180
00:10:43,327 --> 00:10:44,453
You're...

181
00:10:45,538 --> 00:10:46,563
Me?

182
00:10:47,707 --> 00:10:48,749
I'm your...

183
00:10:49,875 --> 00:10:51,001
guardian angel.

184
00:10:53,879 --> 00:10:55,006
Oh my!

185
00:10:56,048 --> 00:10:57,423
You're an angel?!

186
