No wonder you're so beautiful.

187
00:11:01,887 --> 00:11:03,764
Why did you come down to Earth?

188
00:11:05,182 --> 00:11:06,767
Can I see your wings?

189
00:11:07,435 --> 00:11:08,561
Where are your wings?

190
00:11:12,440 --> 00:11:13,941
Can we be friends?

191
00:11:14,984 --> 00:11:16,360
Of course! Seriously!

192
00:11:16,360 --> 00:11:19,196
Why would I say no to being
friends with a real angel?

193
00:11:20,656 --> 00:11:24,702
I'm not literally an angel,
but I'm your guardian angel—

194
00:11:24,702 --> 00:11:25,691
Ma'am Aemie!

195
00:11:26,454 --> 00:11:27,872
Jacob, come here, quick!

196
00:11:28,331 --> 00:11:29,105
Hurry!

197
00:11:32,626 --> 00:11:33,636
Oh no!

198
00:11:34,045 --> 00:11:35,066
Huh?

199
00:11:35,129 --> 00:11:36,213
Where did she go?

200
00:11:36,922 --> 00:11:38,035
The angel?

201
00:11:40,968 --> 00:11:41,802
Where'd she go?

202
00:11:41,802 --> 00:11:43,637
Ma'am, who was that?

203
00:11:44,764 --> 00:11:47,224
Oh, that was my guardian angel.

204
00:11:49,852 --> 00:11:50,603
Why are you here?

205
00:11:51,854 --> 00:11:53,107
Are you here to get
a free meal from me?

206
00:11:53,898 --> 00:11:56,400
