Hey, Jacob!

209
00:12:06,786 --> 00:12:07,553
Hey!

210
00:12:07,578 --> 00:12:08,371
Oh, sorry, ma'am.

211
00:12:08,371 --> 00:12:09,538
Oh, it's Mr. Roswell.

212
00:12:10,206 --> 00:12:11,374
He wants to talk to you.

213
00:12:14,168 --> 00:12:15,086
Hi, Dong.

214
00:12:15,086 --> 00:12:17,338
What on earth have you been up to?

215
00:12:18,631 --> 00:12:20,091
Oh no!

216
00:12:20,549 --> 00:12:21,092
Oh, sorry!

217
00:12:21,092 --> 00:12:23,552
I forgot to charge
my phone again.

218
00:12:23,719 --> 00:12:25,179
Get ready later.

219
00:12:25,179 --> 00:12:26,806
No. Just listen first.

220
00:12:29,600 --> 00:12:31,435
That's not fair!

221
00:12:31,936 --> 00:12:33,646
Why not just tell me now?

222
00:12:35,231 --> 00:12:38,109
