and today is already "tomorrow."

223
00:12:38,109 --> 00:12:39,630
I'll be the one to fetch you later.

224
00:12:39,693 --> 00:12:41,622
So meet me at the
gate. We'll go somewhere.

225
00:12:41,647 --> 00:12:42,988
Really? Okay, okay.

226
00:12:42,988 --> 00:12:43,989
Alright, alright, alright.

227
00:12:44,949 --> 00:12:45,866
Aye, aye, Captain!

228
00:12:48,327 --> 00:12:49,120
Bye-bye, bye-bye.

229
00:12:50,788 --> 00:12:51,789
Oh, Jacob, your phone.

230
00:12:55,334 --> 00:12:56,460
Hey, Jacob, your phone!

231
00:12:56,669 --> 00:12:57,503
Oh, sorry, ma'am.

232
00:12:57,503 --> 00:12:58,212
Thank you.

233
00:12:59,505 --> 00:13:01,757
Ma'am, wasn't that girl pretty?

234
00:13:15,980 --> 00:13:18,315
Here's the entire map
of the Grand Park Hotel.

235
00:13:20,067 --> 00:13:22,736
Your target is the hotel owner.

236
00:13:24,697 --> 00:13:25,865
Alexander Park.

237
00:13:27,158 --> 00:13:30,744
There will be a big transaction
at around 9 in the evening.

238
00:13:31,412 --> 00:13:34,248
So, we only have a
few hours left to prepare.

239
00:13:35,249 --> 00:13:38,043
Do we need a negotiator
for that transaction?

240
00:13:38,043 --> 00:13:39,081
No.

241
00:13:39,962 --> 00:13:42,173
He's going to meet
someone, and we don't care.

242
00:13:42,798 --> 00:13:45,426
Our aim is Young here.

243
00:13:46,135 --> 00:13:48,137
Finish off his target.

244
00:13:48,804 --> 00:13:49,847
Nothing else.

245
00:13:50,264 --> 00:13:51,974
Do we really need
to go with Young?

246
00:13:53,100 --> 00:13:54,727
Just so he can
take out his target?

247
00:13:55,352 --> 00:13:56,534
I mean,

248
00:13:57,188 --> 00:13:58,230
this guy is old enough.

249
00:13:59,023 --> 00:14:00,136
He can handle it.

250
00:14:00,566 --> 00:14:03,152
Don't underestimate
Alexander Park.

251
00:14:03,277 --> 00:14:04,737
According to my sources,

252
00:14:05,196 --> 00:14:06,947
there'll be a lot of guards
at the location later.

253
00:14:07,072 --> 00:14:08,282
The more, the merrier.

254
00:14:09,742 --> 00:14:12,036
Our directive is
to shoot on sight.

255
00:14:12,453 --> 00:14:15,748
Anyone who tries to interfere with
our mission gets a bullet to the head.

256
00:14:16,749 --> 00:14:17,923
And you, Young...

257
00:14:19,793 --> 00:14:21,504
You will focus on your target.

258
00:14:24,215 --> 00:14:25,257
Any questions?

259
00:14:26,634 --> 00:14:27,510
Nah.

260
00:14:27,968 --> 00:14:29,261
I'm good.

261
00:14:29,261 --> 00:14:29,970
Okay.

262
00:14:30,888 --> 00:14:31,388
Good.

263
00:14:31,847 --> 00:14:32,765
Let's get ready.

264
00:14:33,557 --> 00:14:36,644
We need to be there as early
as possible to survey the area.

265
00:14:44,485 --> 00:14:47,404
And remember,
keep your guard up.

266
00:14:48,113 --> 00:14:49,990
We don't know who's going
to be there until we get there.

267
00:14:56,247 --> 00:14:57,373
Shit!

268
00:14:59,041 --> 00:14:59,792
Are you ready?

269
00:15:00,751 --> 00:15:01,877
Are you ready?

270
00:15:02,461 --> 00:15:03,504
How about you,
babe? Are you ready?

271
00:15:03,504 --> 00:15:04,630
I'm so ready.

272
00:15:04,630 --> 00:15:05,464
Let's do this.

273
00:15:05,589 --> 00:15:06,257
You're ready?

274
00:15:07,550 --> 00:15:08,715
Let's go.

275
00:15:15,432 --> 00:15:16,892
Grand Park Hotel.

